      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n\u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\" alt\u003d\"\" /\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eTelecom Customer Experience Improvement\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\nThis app focuses on optimizing network cell performance to enhance overall customer satisfaction. By analyzing call data records (CDRs), tower performance metrics, and user behavior, the app provides real-time insights into network efficiency, coverage quality, and service reliability. The goal is to proactively identify potential network issues, optimize cell performance, and improve customer experience by minimizing call drops and service interruptions.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eUsers provide:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e The start and end date of network data records to be analysed.\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Cell technologies (2G/3G/etc.) they want to target in the analysis\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Type of analysis they want to run (predictive/call drop/cell recommendation)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eThe app delivers:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Detailed analytics of the configured data according to the options selected\u003c/li\u003e\r\n     \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n  \r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e This app can help minimize call drops and service interruptions, leading to a better experience for customers.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e The analytics provided by the app empower telecom operators to make informed decisions based on concrete data regarding network efficiency, coverage, and reliability.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e By identifying and resolving potential issues before they escalate, the app can help reduce the need for reactive maintenance and support, leading to cost savings.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e",
